00:07:50,958 --> 00:07:52,750
Release Dux Stopper.

106
00:07:55,458 --> 00:07:56,750
Miss Kariya!

107
00:07:57,458 --> 00:07:59,666
Please, you have to let
us all go in there too.

108
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:02,791
The reality is that none of
you would be of any help.

109
00:08:02,875 --> 00:08:05,208
What's happening
to Kazuki and others?

110
00:08:05,291 --> 00:08:08,458
I don't need to explain the
details of our tactics to you.

111
00:08:08,541 --> 00:08:10,041
What's going on, Miss Kariya?

112
00:08:10,125 --> 00:08:11,833
You usually answer
the questions we have!

113
