This is different.
We're not at school!

114
00:08:24,333 --> 00:08:25,916
All of them...

115
00:08:26,333 --> 00:08:29,291
What do they think
that they're trying to do?

116
00:08:29,958 --> 00:08:32,541
I can't believe
we're really at war.

117
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,666
Are you there?

