Soshi look!

164
00:14:29,708 --> 00:14:32,333
Did that plane just save us?

165
00:14:32,416 --> 00:14:34,125
Lindwurm's field
of combat is in the

166
00:14:34,208 --> 00:14:36,333
middle of Tatsumiya
Island's direct path.

167
00:14:36,416 --> 00:14:37,958
At this rate, they will
be entering the number

168
00:14:38,041 --> 00:14:40,291
two defense block
in about 5 minutes.

169
00:14:40,375 --> 00:14:42,791
Just what do those two
think they're doing?!

170
00:14:46,375 --> 00:14:48,083
Mrs. Kaname, why don't
we trying changing

171
00:14:48,166 --> 00:14:49,458
the course
of the island?

172
00:14:49,541 --> 00:14:52,083
Because that would
take us over half a day.

173
00:14:59,541 --> 00:15:02,666
All of this is meaningless
unless we destroy the core.

174
00:15:02,750 --> 00:15:06,000
If that's what needs to be
done, I'll go there and do it.

175
00:15:12,416 --> 00:15:14,375
Release me into that thing!

176
00:15:49,833 --> 00:15:52,291
There's been an impact
on the island's surface.

177
00:15:52,375 --> 00:15:53,833
It's inevitable now.

178
00:15:53,916 --> 00:15:56,458
We'll have to blow our cover
if we want to save the island.

179
00:15:56,541 --> 00:15:57,958
Are you sure?: 

180
00:15:58,791 --> 00:16:00,916
Disable the
camouflage surface.

181
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,750
Set up Walle Shield.

182
00:16:26,750 --> 00:16:28,291
Kazuki!

183
00:16:38,416 --> 00:16:39,875
But, that's...

184
00:16:45,916 --> 00:16:49,958
Uh... A song.
I can hear it.

185
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:01,333
What are we hearing?

186
00:17:04,166 --> 00:17:06,625
Do you hear that? Who's singing?

187
00:17:14,708 --> 00:17:16,958
You know what to do, right?

188
00:17:44,541 --> 00:17:46,833
Sphinx type has vanished.

189
00:17:48,708 --> 00:17:52,166
It seems that she
has completely awakened.

190
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:09,125
That island...

191
00:18:09,208 --> 00:18:10,833
Was there an island here before?

192
00:18:10,916 --> 00:18:13,041
I don't see anything on the map.

193
00:18:13,416 --> 00:18:15,250
Recon plane
Young Star 2 reporting

